title: OrgoCards Organic Chemistry Review
description:
PDF copies of Barron&#039;s "OrgoCards", a flashcard-esque study aide designed to break basic organic chemistry into more manageable pieces.

I looked for something like this the whole time I was in Organic. It is an excellent resource and is highly recommended (of course, it&#039;s much more functional to purchase the cards so that you can have them in your hands wherever/whenever you want).
